{"tid":1803094,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"馮盈盈與十優醫生男友分手　曾甜蜜同居為男友「無名」供樓","createTime":"2019-12-30T03:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T13:43:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"33390dacb86d202eb6f2c66fcdef7079d1edc528","tid":1803094,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2529987/Fung_thumb_20191230_S_v2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2529987%2FFung_thumb_20191230_S_v2_1024.jpg&h=d02c0492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馮盈盈與男友分手！2016年港姐冠軍馮盈盈，今天早上（12月30日）在其IG上宣布，與十優醫生男友分手。馮盈盈指，兩人4年來互相勉勵、扶持，經歷許多高低，但往後日子不再是情侶，仍會互相支持對方，令人惋惜！<br />\n<br />\n馮盈盈在其IG中寫下：<br />\n<br />\n從2015年開始<br />\n這四年間我們互相勉勵 互相扶持<br />\n一起經歷許多高高低低<br />\n見證了對方不同階段<br />\n在往後日子<br />\n即使我倆再不是情侶<br />\n我們仍然會支持對方<br />\n也互相祝福各自的將來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2529987/FYY02_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2529987%2FFYY02_1024.png&h=cebbb399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2016年港姐冠軍馮盈盈，入行時已有「粗口港姐」之名。馮盈盈在主持綜藝節目時作風大膽，常在節目中語出驚人，不論衣著打扮、言行舉止均被網民稱為港姐中的MK之最。不過，鏡頭前敢作敢言，努力拼搏，銀幕後的馮盈盈是廿四孝女兒、好家姐，及好女友。<br />\n<br />\n廿四孝女友「無名」為男友供樓<br />\n<br />\n為感激男友對自己及家人的愛護關懷，馮盈盈更不惜為他供樓，更不介意物業沒有加上其名字。她解釋，置業是雙方討論出來的結果，而且男友早已融入家中，成為很重要的一份子，對彼此的關係非常有信心，自己將來也會時常在新居中留宿，因此負責部分首期亦是女朋友應盡的責任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2529987/bkn-20160912165039018-0912_00862_001_02b_1024.jpghttps://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2529987/bkn-20160912165039018-0912_00862_001_02b_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2529987%2Fbkn-20160912165039018-0912_00862_001_02b_1024.jpghttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2529987%2Fbkn-20160912165039018-0912_00862_001_02b_1024.jpg&h=4ad43433&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c859d5f01b3432d551c85d617edbaa086ff1df09","tid":1803094,"uid":168730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:10:56.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02f43bb42bf6f72afce541a074913c55d861f09","tid":1803094,"uid":124114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"下位老細係？"},{"pid":"44d7862d5abb04a82b3e1ef9374a7995b8d7b530","tid":1803094,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:15:14.000Z","msg":"搵到好碼頭<br />\n<br />\n棄舊愛 港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197015e227e2c82a84e7afdfc5f3af83b6936e23","tid":1803094,"uid":55941,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:17:24.000Z","msg":"FYY飛十優醫生<br />\n定<br />\n十優醫生飛FYY <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d58492c33cb332dbb461d8ef14dfe05ff5e06d","tid":1803094,"uid":68556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"或者對雙方都好。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8c67de6950fb08bd5bbfe22464d413b396648e","tid":1803094,"uid":326580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:24:32.000Z","msg":"結婚前一定要同居 媽媽有教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556cbbbb02e315903c32f5865a4574727b9b29c0","tid":1803094,"uid":133529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:25:06.000Z","msg":"屌到反哂皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c215da8a6d91ce0ccf